<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8CTypesof=
Information">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Types of Information</strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Information is <strong>processed data</strong> that is meaningful and us=
eful for decision-making.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Different types of information serve <strong>different purposes</strong>=
 in organizations or systems.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3=
BasedonNature">1=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 <strong>Based on Nature</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"25=
feefa6-c733-4307-b241-54a420888a5c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Quantitative</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Numeric information that can be measured</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sales numbers, temperature, age</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Qualitative</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Descriptive information that cannot be measured numerically</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Customer feedback, product reviews</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-2=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3=
BasedonTime">2=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 <strong>Based on Time</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"59=
c63408-2adf-41f0-b407-5152d0fbc346" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Real-time / Current</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Information available immediately</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Stock price ticker, live traffic updates</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Historical / Past</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Information from past events</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Last month=E2=80=99s sales report, attendance history</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3=
BasedonSource">3=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 <strong>Based on Source</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"f4=
b7ea23-8b46-4b35-8357-b11e2fb6a459" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Internal</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Generated within the organization</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Employee data, internal reports</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>External</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Comes from outside the organization</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Market research, government statistics</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3=
BasedonPurpose">4=EF=B8=8F=E2=83=A3 <strong>Based on Purpose</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"fc=
024f19-f07c-489b-bba2-4a0a02887f8e" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Strategic</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Long-term planning and decisions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Business expansion plan, investment strategy</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Tactical / Managerial</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Medium-term decisions for departments or projects</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Project scheduling, resource allocation</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Operational / Transactional</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Day-to-day operational decisions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Inventory updates, employee shift schedules</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8CQualiti=
esofGoodInformation">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>Qualities of Good Information</st=
rong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Information is <strong>useful</strong> only if it has certain <strong>qu=
alities</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b1=
bb4c7a-196b-4615-b710-062078e00b25" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Quality</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Accuracy</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Correct and error-free</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Correct employee salary data</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Relevance</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pertinent to the decision at hand</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Customer complaints relevant to product improvement</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Completeness</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Contains all necessary details</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Full report of monthly sales</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Timeliness</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Available when needed</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Real-time stock market data</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Reliability / Credibility</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>From trustworthy sources</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Government census data</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Understandability / Clarity</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Easy to interpret and comprehend</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dashboard with clear charts</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Consistency</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Information does not contradict other data</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Sales numbers match accounting records</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Easily retrievable by authorized users</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Cloud-based database accessible remotely</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=E2=9C=85SummaryTab=
le">=E2=9C=85 <strong>Summary Table</strong></h3>
