<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Details / Examples</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Types of Information</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Quantitative, Qualitative, Real-time, Historical, Internal, External, St=
rategic, Tactical, Operational</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Qualities of Information</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Accuracy, Relevance, Completeness, Timeliness, Reliability, Understandab=
ility, Consistency, Accessibility</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<p>=F0=9F=92=A1 <strong>Tip:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Always ensure information is <strong>accurate, timely, and relevant</str=
ong>, otherwise decisions based on it may fail.</p></li>
</ul>
