<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C1.Proje=
ctManagementConceptsinSoftwareEngineering">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>1. Project =
Management Concepts in Software Engineering</strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Software Project Management (SPM)</strong> is the application of=
 <strong>management principles to software development</strong> to ensure p=
rojects are delivered on time, within budget, and meet quality requirements=
.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-KeyConceptsofSoftwa=
reProjectManagement"><strong>Key Concepts of Software Project Management</s=
trong></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"4a=
132268-435f-4fc9-8157-faf6d787ce1c" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Concept</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Explanation</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Project</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Temporary endeavor to create a unique software product</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Developing an e-commerce website</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Project Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Planning, organizing, monitoring, and controlling resources to achieve g=
oals</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Using Gantt charts, Agile boards</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Scope Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Define and control what is included/excluded in the project</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Determining features of a banking app</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Time Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Estimate, schedule, and control project timelines</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Using CPM or PERT for task scheduling</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Cost Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Estimating, budgeting, and controlling costs</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Budgeting server, development, and testing costs</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Quality Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ensuring software meets functional and non-functional requirements</p></=
td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Implementing testing and code reviews</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Identify, analyze, and mitigate potential risks</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Risk: Server downtime =E2=86=92 Mitigation: Backup server</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Resource Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Managing human resources, tools, and infrastructure</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Assigning developers, testers, and designers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Communication Management</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ensuring proper information flow among team and stakeholders</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Daily standups, weekly reports</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C2.Softw=
areProcessandProjectMetrics">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>2. Software Process and P=
roject Metrics</strong></h1>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-SoftwareProcess"><s=
trong>Software Process</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>A <strong>structured set of activities</strong> to develop software, inc=
luding <strong>specification, design, implementation, testing, and maintena=
nce</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Examples of <strong>Software Process Models</strong>:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Waterfall Model</p></li>
<li>
<p>Agile Model</p></li>
<li>
<p>Spiral Model</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Key Activities in Software Process:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Requirements gathering</p></li>
<li>
<p>Design</p></li>
<li>
<p>Implementation / Coding</p></li>
<li>
<p>Testing</p></li>
<li>
<p>Deployment &amp; Maintenance</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-SoftwareProjectMetr=
ics"><strong>Software Project Metrics</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Metrics are <strong>quantitative measures</strong> to assess software pr=
ocesses, quality, and productivity.</p></li>
</ul>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"c9=
6c65b4-f83f-4cf0-8abc-a211f3baf0af" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Metric Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description &amp; Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Product Metrics</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Measure attributes of software product (e.g., size, complexity) <strong>=
Example:</strong> Lines of Code (LOC), Function Points</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Process Metrics</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Measure effectiveness of development process <strong>Example:</strong> D=
efect density, effort estimation accuracy</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Project Metrics</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Measure project progress and performance <strong>Example:</strong> Sched=
ule variance, cost variance</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Quality Metrics</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Measure quality aspects of software <strong>Example:</strong> Number of =
defects per KLOC, mean time to failure</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>If a module has 2000 lines of code and 10 defects =E2=86=92 defect densi=
ty =3D 10 / 2 =3D 5 defects/KLOC</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C3.Softw=
areProjectPlanning">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>3. Software Project Planning</stro=
ng></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Planning defines <strong>how a software project will be executed, monito=
red, and controlled</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-KeyActivitiesinProj=
ectPlanning"><strong>Key Activities in Project Planning</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Define Objectives:</strong> Identify goals, scope, deliverables.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Estimate Resources:</strong> Team, hardware, software, tools.</p=
></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Effort Estimation:</strong> Predict person-hours required (e.g.,=
 using COCOMO model).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Schedule Development:</strong> Break project into tasks, assign =
dependencies, and prepare timelines (Gantt chart / PERT chart).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Risk Planning:</strong> Identify potential risks and mitigation =
strategies.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Budgeting:</strong> Estimate cost of resources, licenses, infras=
tructure.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Staffing Plan:</strong> Assign developers, testers, designers, m=
anagers.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-ExampleofProjectPla=
nning"><strong>Example of Project Planning</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Project:</strong> Online Banking System</p>
