<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C1.RiskA=
nalysisandManagement">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>1. Risk Analysis and Management<=
/strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Risk</strong>: Any event or condition that could negatively affe=
ct the project=E2=80=99s objectives (time, cost, quality).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Risk Management</strong>: Identifying, analyzing, prioritizing, =
and mitigating risks to minimize impact.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-StepsinRiskManageme=
nt"><strong>Steps in Risk Management</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"ae=
0e5108-dbb5-4291-b645-591d2d864708" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Step</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Identification</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Identify potential risks in project</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Delay in requirement approval, server crash</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Analysis</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Evaluate likelihood and impact</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Likely delay: 2 weeks, High impact on delivery</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Prioritization</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rank risks based on severity</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>High: server downtime, Medium: resource shortage</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Mitigation / Planning</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Plan how to prevent or reduce risk</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Backup servers, hire temporary developers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Risk Monitoring</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Continuously track risks during project</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Weekly risk review meetings</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-TypesofRisksinSoftw=
areProjects"><strong>Types of Risks in Software Projects</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"fc=
44715a-8eb9-4ef9-8f4c-a620865fd5bf" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Type</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Technical Risks</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Problems with technology or tools</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>New programming language, software bugs</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Project Management Risks</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Delays or scope creep</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Tasks taking longer than estimated</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Organizational Risks</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Lack of resources or support</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Team unavailable due to other projects</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>External Risks</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Outside the organization</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Changes in government regulations, market shifts</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-RiskAnalysisTechniq=
ues"><strong>Risk Analysis Techniques</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Qualitative Risk Analysis</strong>: Prioritize risks based on <s=
trong>impact and probability</strong> (High, Medium, Low).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Quantitative Risk Analysis</strong>: Assign numeric values to ri=
sk probability and impact to calculate <strong>Expected Monetary Value (EMV=
)</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Example (EMV calculation):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Probability of server crash =3D 0.1 (10%)</p></li>
<li>
<p>Impact =3D $10,000</p></li>
<li>
<p>EMV =3D 0.1 =C3=97 $10,000 =3D $1,000</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C2.Proje=
ctSchedulingandTracking">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>2. Project Scheduling and Tra=
cking</strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Project Scheduling</strong>: Defining <strong>tasks, duration, s=
equence, and dependencies</strong> for timely project completion.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Project Tracking</strong>: Monitoring progress, identifying devi=
ations, and taking corrective actions.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-KeyActivitiesinProj=
ectScheduling"><strong>Key Activities in Project Scheduling</strong></h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Task Breakdown</strong>: Divide project into smaller tasks (Work=
 Breakdown Structure - WBS)</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Estimate Duration</strong>: Predict time required for each task<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Sequence Tasks</strong>: Identify task dependencies</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Assign Resources</strong>: Allocate team members, tools, and bud=
get</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Prepare Schedule</strong>: Use charts like <strong>Gantt Chart</=
strong>, <strong>PERT/CPM</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<hr>
