</ol>
<p>Perfect! Let=E2=80=99s break it down clearly and systematically. We=E2=
=80=99ll cover <strong>Sequential Waterfall Life Cycle</strong> and <strong=
>Inception Phase</strong>.</p>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C1.Seque=
ntialWaterfallLifeCycle">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>1. Sequential Waterfall Life =
Cycle</strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>The <strong>Waterfall Model</strong> is a <strong>linear and sequential =
software development life cycle</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Each phase must be <strong>completed before the next begins</strong>.</p=
></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-PhasesoftheWaterfal=
lModel"><strong>Phases of the Waterfall Model</strong></h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"c2=
513325-050b-401e-a27a-1914dd7bf920" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Phase</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Requirement Analysis</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Gather and document what the software should do</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>SRS document for a banking app</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>System Design</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Define system architecture, components, data models</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>UML diagrams, DB schema for the app</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Implementation / Coding</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Translate design into code</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Develop login, transactions, account modules</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Testing</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Verify system works correctly and meets requirements</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Unit testing, system testing</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Deployment</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Release the software to users</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Install on client servers or cloud</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Maintenance</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Fix bugs and enhance features after deployment</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Adding new payment methods or fixing login issues</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p><strong>Key Characteristics:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Linear and rigid</strong>: No overlap between phases</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Documentation-heavy</strong>: Each phase produces formal deliver=
ables</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Best for</strong>: Well-understood projects with fixed requireme=
nts</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Advantages:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Simple and easy to manage</p></li>
<li>
<p>Clear milestones for each phase</p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Disadvantages:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Inflexible to requirement changes</p></li>
<li>
<p>Late detection of defects (in testing phase)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-WaterfallModelDiagr=
am"><strong>Waterfall Model Diagram</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">Require=
ments =E2=86=92 Design =E2=86=92 Implementation =E2=86=92 Testing =E2=86=92=
 Deployment =E2=86=92 Maintenance
</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr>
<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=93=8C2.Incep=
tionPhase(UnifiedProcess/IterativeApproach)">=F0=9F=93=8C <strong>2. Incept=
ion Phase (Unified Process / Iterative Approach)</strong></h1>
<p><strong>Definition:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>The <strong>Inception Phase</strong> is the <strong>first phase of itera=
tive development</strong> (Unified Process, RUP).</p></li>
<li>
<p>Purpose: <strong>Determine project scope, feasibility, and high-level re=
quirements</strong>.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-KeyActivitiesinInce=
ptionPhase"><strong>Key Activities in Inception Phase</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"14=
6a9864-1605-4174-80bd-dccdcb132518" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Activity</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Description</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Stakeholder Identification</strong></p></td>
