<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Business owner, product manager</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Requirement Elicitation</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Collect high-level functional &amp; non-functional requirements</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>=E2=80=9CUsers can browse products and make purchases online=E2=80=9D</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
