<p>Identify potential project risks</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>New technology, tight deadlines</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>High-Level Use Cases</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Define main system interactions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>=E2=80=9CCustomer places order=E2=80=9D, =E2=80=9CAdmin updates inventor=
y=E2=80=9D</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Project Estimation</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rough cost, time, and resource estimates</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>6-month development with 5 developers</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-OutputsofInceptionP=
hase"><strong>Outputs of Inception Phase</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Initial vision document</p></li>
<li>
<p>Project scope and objectives</p></li>
<li>
<p>Initial use cases</p></li>
<li>
<p>High-level risk list</p></li>
<li>
<p>Rough project plan and budget</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h3 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-InceptionvsWaterfal=
lRequirementsPhase"><strong>Inception vs Waterfall Requirements Phase</stro=
ng></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8a=
baa583-43ee-46f5-b41e-6032771607c2" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Aspect</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Waterfall Requirement Analysis</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Inception Phase (Iterative/UP)</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Scope</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Full detailed requirements</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>High-level scope only</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Flexibility</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Rigid</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Flexible to change</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
