<p><strong>Waterfall</strong> is great for <strong>stable, well-understood =
projects</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Inception Phase</strong> is part of <strong>iterative developmen=
t</strong>, ideal for projects with <strong>uncertain requirements</strong>=
.</p></li>
</ul>
