<p>Test individual functions/classes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>JUnit test for <code>add()</code> method</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Integration Testing</strong></p></td>
