<p>Test interactions between modules</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>LoginService</code> + <code>DatabaseService</code></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Validation Testing</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Check if system meets requirements</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Invalid login test</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>System Testing</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Test full system (functional &amp; non-functional)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>E-commerce workflow test</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Debugging</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Find and fix errors after testing</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Handling division by zero</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
