<p><strong>MTTR</strong> =E2=86=92 How long it takes to fix failures (lower=
 =3D better).</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Safety-critical systems</strong> require <strong>redundancy, fai=
l-safe mechanisms, and rigorous testing</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
