<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=94=B92.Metri=
csforSourceCode">=F0=9F=94=B9 <strong>2. Metrics for Source Code</strong></=
h1>
<p>These metrics <strong>measure quality, complexity, and maintainability o=
f code</strong>.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"71=
f33aab-8522-45d0-8e67-0e78953673ce" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Metric</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Definition</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Example / Use</p></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Lines of Code (LOC)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Total lines in program (excluding comments)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Java file has 500 LOC</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Cyclomatic Complexity (CC)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Independent paths through code (McCabe metric)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><code>if-else</code> + <code>for loop</code> =3D CC =3D 3</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>BANG Metrics</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
