</td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Java function =E2=86=92 B =3D 1, A =3D 2, N =3D 1, G =3D 0 =E2=86=92 BAN=
G =3D 4</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Code Coverage</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>% of code executed by tests (statement, branch, path)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>80% code coverage =E2=86=92 20% code untested</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Comment Density</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ratio of comment lines to code lines</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>50 comment lines / 500 LOC =3D 10%</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>=E2=9C=85 <strong>Purpose:</strong> Evaluate <strong>complexity, readabi=
lity, maintainability, and defect-proneness</strong> of code.</p>
