<h1 id=3D"SoftwareEngineeringandInformationSystemDesign-=F0=9F=94=B93.Metri=
csforTesting">=F0=9F=94=B9 <strong>3. Metrics for Testing</strong></h1>
<p>Testing metrics <strong>measure effectiveness of testing and quality of =
software</strong>.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"54=
437613-7848-47e4-a003-e810143cc72a" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Metric</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p>Definition</p></th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">
