<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>5 defects / 1000 LOC =3D 0.005</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Defect Removal Efficiency (DRE)</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
