<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>MTBF =3D 200 hours for e-commerce checkout</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Number of Test Cases Executed / Passed / Failed</strong></p></td=
>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
