<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Executed =3D 100, Passed =3D 95, Failed =3D 5</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>=E2=9C=85 <strong>Purpose:</strong> Track <strong>effectiveness of testi=
ng, identify risk areas, and improve quality</strong>.</p>
